very significantly.

151
00:09:23,699 --> 00:09:26,564
In fact, I can keep going down in energy

152
00:09:26,564 --> 00:09:29,469
and the cross-section
will become much, much larger,

153
00:09:30,176 --> 00:09:32,335
So I need to slow down
the neutrons in order to arrive

154
00:09:32,335 --> 00:09:36,393
at an optimal breeding of the tritium.

